---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<main>
			<h1>👦🏻🏃🏻💵 Olá Turma!</h1>
			<p>
				Bem vindo ao meu site feito em <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a>! Esse
				modelo serve para o trabalho de tópicos especiais em informática, como um ponto de partida leve e com estilo minimalista para quem deseja
				criar um site pessoal, blog ou portfólio com o Astro.
			</p>
			<p>
				Este modelo vem com algumas integrações já configuradas em seu arquivo
				<code>astro.config.mjs</code> file. Você pode personalizar sua configuração com
				<a href="https://astro.build/integrations">Astro Integrations</a> para adicionar ferramentas como Tailwind, React ou Vue ao seu projeto.
			</p>
			<p>
				Divirta-se, e caso tenha duvidas, <a href="https://docs.astro.build/"
					>leia as documentações</a> ou junte-se no servidor da comunidade do astro no <a href="https://astro.build/chat"> Discord</a> caso tenha duvidas.
			</p>
			<p>
		</main>

		<svg class="waves" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320">
			<path fill="#f041ff" fill-opacity="1" class="wave-1" d="M0,64L24,96C48,128,96,192,144,213.3C192,235,240,213,288,186.7C336,160,384,128,432,133.3C480,139,528,181,576,181.3C624,181,672,139,720,117.3C768,96,816,96,864,96C912,96,960,96,1008,106.7C1056,117,1104,139,1152,138.7C1200,139,1248,117,1296,128C1344,139,1392,181,1416,202.7L1440,224L1440,320L1416,320C1392,320,1344,320,1296,320C1248,320,1200,320,1152,320C1104,320,1056,320,1008,320C960,320,912,320,864,320C816,320,768,320,720,320C672,320,624,320,576,320C528,320,480,320,432,320C384,320,336,320,288,320C240,320,192,320,144,320C96,320,48,320,24,320L0,320Z"></path>
			
			<path fill="#e7008a" fill-opacity="1" class="wave-2" d="M0,256L48,229.3C96,203,192,149,288,106.7C384,64,480,32,576,21.3C672,11,768,21,864,58.7C960,96,1056,160,1152,176C1248,192,1344,160,1392,144L1440,128L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
			
			<path fill="#9543e8" fill-opacity="1" class="wave-3" d="M0,96L48,106.7C96,117,192,139,288,122.7C384,107,480,53,576,64C672,75,768,149,864,181.3C960,213,1056,203,1152,181.3C1248,160,1344,128,1392,112L1440,96L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
		</svg>

		<style>
			.waves{
				position:block;
				bottom:0;
				left:0;
				right:0;
				z-index:-1000;

			}
			.wave-1{
				animation: movewave1 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
				transform:scaleX(1.1);
			}

			.wave-2{
				animation: movewave2 5s 1.2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
				transform:scaleX(1.1);
			}

			.wave-3{
				animation: movewave3 7s 0.7s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
				transform:scaleX(1.1);
			}

			@keyframes movewave1{
				from{
					transform:translateX(0px);
				}
			}

			
			@keyframes movewave2{
				from{
					transform:translateX(0px);
				}
			}

			@keyframes movewave3{
				from{
					transform:translateX(0px);
				}
			}

			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				ul {
					gap: 0.5em;
				}
				ul li {
					width: 100%;
					text-align: center;
				}
				ul li:first-child {
					margin-bottom: 0;
				}
				ul li:first-child .title {
					font-size: 1.563em;
				}
			}
		</style>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
